OL,5,G1200 Car Pound Cops: Give Me My Car...
OL,6,     F...Back! Following car recovery
OL,7,     Fcompanies that are tasked with
OL,8,     Ftaking illegal, unroadworthy,
OL,9,     Funtaxed, uninsured vehicles off
OL,10,     Fthe road and ensuring their owners
OL,11,     Fpay the penalty.
OL,12,G1300 Traffic Cops
OL,13,     FBurglary is one of the hardest
OL,14,     Fcrimes to secure a conviction for.
OL,15,     FIn this episode, the cops target
OL,16,     Fthieves and burglars who steal
OL,17,     Ffrom our homes, vehicles and
OL,18,     Fbusinesses.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
