OL,5,G1600 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FMore than 60 thefts are reported
OL,7,     Fto Derbyshire Police every day. In
OL,8,     Fthis episode, following a rise in
OL,9,     Fthefts across the East Midlands,
OL,10,     Fofficers target organised gangs of
OL,11,     Fthieves.
OL,12,G1700 Police Interceptors
OL,13,     FDog handler Martyn finds himself
OL,14,     Fin the firing line when he cops a
OL,15,     Ftasty right hook and Dan is given
OL,16,     Fthe runaround by an uninsured
OL,17,     Fdriver.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
