OL,5,G1800 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FDocumentary series. The
OL,7,     Finterceptors of Durham and
OL,8,     FCleveland tackle a stand-off
OL,9,     Fbetween armed officers and a
OL,10,     Fdangerous knifeman and a man
OL,11,     Fwielding a length of guttering.
OL,12,G1900 Police Interceptors
OL,13,     FInterceptors are called to an
OL,14,     Femergency landing at Durham Tees
OL,15,     FValley Airport.
OL,16,G2000 Police Interceptors
OL,17,     FKev Salter and Ian Squire hunt for
OL,18,     Fa man roaming the late-night
OL,19,     Fstreets with a machete.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
