OL,5,G2100 The Surgeon
OL,6,     FBehind the surgeon's mask - from
OL,7,     Fthe pressurised operating theatre
OL,8,     Fto life at home - as consultant
OL,9,     Fheart surgeon Inder Birdi faces
OL,10,     Fone of the most challenging cases
OL,11,     Fof his career.
OL,12,G2200 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,13,     FAdam, 42, has a broken leg after a
OL,14,     Ffall at work, 22-year-old Luke has
OL,15,     Fa potentially life-threatening
OL,16,     Firregular heartbeat, and a child
OL,17,     Fstops breathing after a seizure.
