OL,5,G2300 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,6,     FCritical care teams race to save
OL,7,     Flives as a 61-year-old is injured
OL,8,     Fin a motorcycle crash, a new mum
OL,9,     Fhaemorrhages days after giving
OL,10,     Fbirth, and a 12-year-old suffers
OL,11,     Fsevere leg injuries.
OL,12,G0000 A&E After Dark
OL,13,     FA patient brought into A&E by
OL,14,     Fpolice claims to have swallowed
OL,15,     Fdrugs, but he refuses to
OL,16,     Fco-operate with staff, putting the
OL,17,     FNHS under further pressure.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
